These are Puzzles for 6x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x6-Level-2-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: tea, iced-tea, juice, almond-milk, cola, lemonade
City: marseilles, rome, nizza, miami, berlin, colone
House: palace, art-deco, wooden, tower, futuristic, ranch-style
6 different pets are kept: fish, frog, goat, goldfish, snake, turtle
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, parkour, rowing, surfing, water-polo
The people have 6 different jobs:  dressmaker, chef, musician, electrician, dancer, mechanic
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is the chef##1
 2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the wooden house##1
 3. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
 4. the art-deco house is on the right of the dancer##1
 5. the palace house is on the far left##1
 6. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the chef##1
 7. the person traveling to berlin is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person drinking juice is on the right of the electrician##1
 9. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
10. the owner of the snake is the person drinking iced-tea##1
11. the person traveling to berlin is on the far right##1
12. the owner of the goat is between the art-deco house and the owner of the goldfish##2
13. the person who's sport is rowing is the owner of the frog##1
14. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the electrician##1
15. the owner of the snake is the person who's sport is cricket##1
16. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
17. the mechanic is on the right of the futuristic house##1
18. the electrician is the person drinking tea##1
19. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the wooden house##1
20. the dressmaker is on the far left##1
21. the electrician is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
22. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
23. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
24. the person who's sport is surfing is the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |    5     |     6      |
